WEBVTT

00:00:05.553 --> 00:00:09.318
These are sequences from a play called
"The Lehman Trilogy,"

00:00:09.342 --> 00:00:14.384
which traces the origins
of Western capitalism

00:00:14.408 --> 00:00:15.827
in three hours,

00:00:15.851 --> 00:00:18.306
with three actors and a piano.

00:00:19.356 --> 00:00:23.185
And my role was to create a stage design

00:00:23.209 --> 00:00:26.723
to write a visual language for this work.

00:00:27.699 --> 00:00:30.983
The play describes Atlantic crossings,